  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> <u>The mysterious beginning</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a cold dungeon—dizzy, confused, and not alone. A voice calls to you from the dark, promising freedom. You take the lantern and step out, but a question lingers: should you trust him?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> <u>Step into the Mirrors</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirrors are scattered across the dungeon—gateways into haunting memories. Solving their twisted puzzles might let you out… or trap you deeper in guilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Reflections of Sin</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mirror reveals the memories of those who came before with different experience and mechanics. Through notes and mysterious scenes, you’ll uncover who they were and what they did. Let their deeds and fate guide the forging of your own destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/edd56fdde9671aa05c21f025c1a63e4f.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/edd56fdde9671aa05c21f025c1a63e4f.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/edd56fdde9671aa05c21f025c1a63e4f.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>The Maze of Insanity</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you reach the second part of the dungeon, you find yourself in a maze. You’re not the first one here. Those who ran out of time lost their sanity, and now they wander as tormented souls. Find pills to stay sane, and hide from what hunts you in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/517920b9def516f75365349c3f5472a2.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/517920b9def516f75365349c3f5472a2.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/517920b9def516f75365349c3f5472a2.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Every mistake leaves a scar</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depending on your actions in different parts of the dungeon and the memories of others, you'll uncover multiple endings. Remember: the easiest route won’t always lead to the best ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you escape your fate, or will your sins consume you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/bfb32540ec272550fb732221a3acf144.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/bfb32540ec272550fb732221a3acf144.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/bfb32540ec272550fb732221a3acf144.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Features</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark, narrative-driven psychological experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by real criminal cases</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surreal and symbolic environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Themes of guilt, sin, and redemption</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric sound design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery and puzzle-solving</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth and escape sequences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replayable gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e04f8fe557ce8f1f7dbb1a622d1242b6.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e04f8fe557ce8f1f7dbb1a622d1242b6.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e04f8fe557ce8f1f7dbb1a622d1242b6.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to enter <i>Satan's Dungeon</i> and uncover the truth hidden within?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> <u>The mysterious beginning</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a cold dungeon—dizzy, confused, and not alone. A voice calls to you from the dark, promising freedom. You take the lantern and step out, but a question lingers: should you trust him?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> <u>Step into the Mirrors</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirrors are scattered across the dungeon—gateways into haunting memories. Solving their twisted puzzles might let you out… or trap you deeper in guilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.webm?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/e725ba623f9ae2d31e8149d966eea4d8.mp4?t=1764281980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Reflections of Sin</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mirror reveals the memories of those who came before with different experience and mechanics. Through notes and mysterious scenes, you’ll uncover who they were and what they did. Let their deeds and fate guide the forging of your own destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437110/extras/edd56fdde9671aa05c21f025c1a63e4f.poster.avif?t=1764281980\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap